# 🧭 SYSTEM PRINCIPLE

All operations are managed under:

```
SITE LOCATION
```

Each Site Location contains:

* One Assistant Supervisor
* Surveyor
* Drivers (Truck / Machine)
* Assigned Trucks
* Assigned Machines
* Allocated Budget

Assistant Supervisor becomes:

👉 Local Budget Controller
👉 Expense Owner
👉 Fuel Usage Responsible
👉 Driver Allocator

